lead_paragraph: Roger Federer ramped his game up another level in a clinically efficient 7-6(4) 6-2 6-4 win over sixth seed Tomas Berdych on Tuesday and advance to his 12th Australian Open semi-final.

headline.print_headline: Federer Ramps Game Up to Move Into Semis
